#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "sn12.64:6.1"
msgid "Kabaḷīkāre ce, bhikkhave, āhāre natthi rāgo natthi nandī natthi taṇhā, appatiṭṭhitaṃ tattha viññāṇaṃ avirūḷhaṃ. "
msgstr "If there is no desire, relishing, and craving for solid food, consciousness does not become established there and doesn’t grow. "

