#. REF: sc8
#. VAR: kvāssa patiṭṭhitā → kvassa patiṭṭhitā (pts1-2) | kattha patiṭṭhitā (mr)
msgctxt "sn12.64:8.1"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, kūṭāgāraṃ vā kūṭāgārasālaṃ vā uttarāya vā dakkhiṇāya vā pācīnāya vā vātapānā sūriye uggacchante vātapānena rasmi pavisitvā kvāssa patiṭṭhitā”ti? "
msgstr "Suppose there was a bungalow or a hall with a peaked roof, with windows on the northern, southern, or eastern side. When the sun rises and a ray of light enters through a window, where would it land?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.64:8.2"
msgid "“Pacchimāyaṃ, bhante, bhittiyan”ti. "
msgstr "“On the western wall, sir.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.64:8.3"
msgid "“Pacchimā ce, bhikkhave, bhitti nāssa kvāssa patiṭṭhitā”ti? "
msgstr "“If there was no western wall, where would it land?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.64:8.4"
msgid "“Pathaviyaṃ, bhante”ti. "
msgstr "“On the ground, sir.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.64:8.5"
msgid "“Pathavī ce, bhikkhave, nāssa kvāssa patiṭṭhitā”ti? "
msgstr "“If there was no ground, where would it land?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.64:8.6"
msgid "“Āpasmiṃ, bhante”ti. "
msgstr "“In water, sir.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.64:8.7"
msgid "“Āpo ce, bhikkhave, nāssa kvāssa patiṭṭhitā”ti? "
msgstr "“If there was no water, where would it land?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.64:8.8"
msgid "“Appatiṭṭhitā, bhante”ti. "
msgstr "“It wouldn’t land, sir.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.64:8.9"
msgid "“Evameva kho, bhikkhave, kabaḷīkāre ce āhāre natthi rāgo natthi nandī natthi taṇhā … pe …. "
msgstr "“In the same way, if there is no desire, relishing, and craving for solid food, consciousness does not become established there and doesn’t grow. … "

